description: Protect your investment with a Plasma TPU Case from Infinite Products. The high quality Plasma Case was made specifically to fit your iPod touch 5G. Precise cut outs allow access to all functions of your iPod touch 5G while protecting it from bumps and scratches. Combine the shock protection from a silicone case, with the durability of a hard case!
title: Infinite Products Plasma TPU Jelly Case for iPod touch 5G (Black)
